{"tid":941933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"偷拍6歲女童裙底！男大生「腿夾手機」辯：她鞋好看","createTime":"2018-12-15T08:35:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T13:36:30.000Z","uid":35468,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b4a13f945ddb16dbfc072a259f2595f89e932b16","tid":941933,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T08:35:52.000Z","msg":"偷拍6歲女童裙底！男大生「腿夾手機」辯：她鞋好看<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/upload/2018/08/22/20180822221340-bb9cafe8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F22%2F20180822221340-bb9cafe8.jpg&h=9e2789ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n示意圖／TVBS<br />\n<br />\n又有偷拍狼！新北市一名媽媽表示，他們一家四口上餐館用餐，發現隔壁桌一名男子似乎在偷拍6歲女兒裙底，仔細觀察後果然聽到快門聲，女童父母當場要男子交出手機，竟發現裡頭有多達14張女童腿部的照片，立刻報警處理，而男大生被逮後，供稱覺得女童的鞋子很好看，才拍著好玩。<br />\n<br />\n帶孩子吃個飯竟遇上偷拍狼！女童媽媽指控，當天全家人帶著6歲女兒到餐廳吃飯，後頭一名黑色上衣的男子跟著入店，兩組人就坐在隔壁桌。當時男子將手機夾在大腿之間固定，再按下錄影，想要偷拍隔壁女童的裙底，沒想到相機聲露餡，當場被女童父母識破，氣得報警逮人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/upload/2018/08/22/20180822221337-96f0d966.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F22%2F20180822221337-96f0d966.jpg&h=33538d11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n示意圖／TVBS<br />\n<br />\n警方調查，該名偷拍男士名大四生，他供稱當天覺得女童的鞋子很好看，相機剛好有問題就搖了一下，只是好玩，回家就會刪掉，但沒想到被誤會，也承認偷拍可能造成對方不舒服，但覺得沒嚴重到要提告。<br />\n<br />\n不過手機裡滿滿14張女童腿部特寫，讓爸媽看了氣壞了，指控男大生被逮時說一時刺激好玩，卻又改口說相機出問題，說法反覆，也讓女童心中留下陰影，父母堅決提告絕不姑息。"},{"pid":"0720907bf6236edb23a1a2126ee28a4249ef17b3","tid":941933,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T08:36:32.000Z","msg":"又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f2a8754ae37e90ed2f2e5f17dee66230564e333","tid":941933,"uid":116330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T08:45:05.000Z","msg":"所以咪話"},{"pid":"99dba483b95ba715091f377010c7cd8e26652147","tid":941933,"uid":143241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T08:50:31.000Z","msg":"啲圖係咩事啊？！"},{"pid":"b49e5df599af2e070dd168a8a79876ffd29f896b","tid":941933,"uid":155199,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T08:58:27.000Z","msg":"高質素TVBS示意圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f9d4a02b2d2b6fb67fed936c60c6a94c2db5bd","tid":941933,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99dba483b95ba715091f377010c7cd8e26652147","tid":941933,"uid":143241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T08:50:31.000Z","msg":"啲圖係咩事啊？！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T08:59:21.000Z","msg":"示意圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bcbcdd2afc7c07f4356b44992b7692ea74bef3d","tid":941933,"uid":34685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T09:38:33.000Z","msg":"新北市"},{"pid":"5cfcb42e17b02c2868e7bab8b12945510576e7f3","tid":941933,"uid":47954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T13:36:30.000Z","msg":"新北得分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}